  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个AXI4从设备读通道监控器的架构图。整体结构我想分成三层：前端捕获、事务监控、还有过滤输出。最外层是标准的AXI4 Slave Interface。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI4 Slave Interface",
        "axi4_slave_rd_mon"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，AXI4读通道的话，应该包含AR和R两个通道对吧？AR是从master过来的读地址，R是返回的数据。这两个都要连到前端？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR Channel",
        "R Channel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AR和R都要进前端。前端这块我们叫AXI4 Slave Frontend，它要支持一个特性：data-before-addr，就是数据可能比地址先到的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frontend",
        "Signal capture",
        "Data-before-addr support"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出外层AXI4 Slave Interface，里面放上AR Channel和R Channel，然后右边画axi4_slave_rd_mon这个大框，第一层Frontend画进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI4 Slave Interface",
        "AR Channel",
        "R Channel",
        "axi4_slave_rd_mon",
        "Frontend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Frontend下面接监控层，这部分继承自axi_monitor_base，要做transaction tracking和timeout detection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitor",
        "axi_monitor_base",
        "Transaction tracking",
        "Timeout detection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Monitor作为第二层子图，放在Frontend下面。然后第三层是过滤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitor",
        "Filter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，第三层叫axi_monitor_filtered，专门做packet filtering。三层是串行关系：Frontend → Monitor → Filter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axi_monitor_filtered",
        "Packet filtering"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三层都画好了，数据流从上到下。最后输出到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frontend",
        "Monitor",
        "Filter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "输出到Monitor Bus，数据格式是monbus_packet，位宽64位。这个作为最右侧的输出子图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitor Bus",
        "monbus_packet[63:0]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Monitor Bus子图画在最右边，里面放monbus_packet[63:0]。现在我把所有连线补上：AR和R都指向Frontend，Frontend到Monitor，Monitor到Filter，Filter到MONBUS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR Channel",
        "R Channel",
        "Frontend",
